<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
to [person in same room with you] [message] : sends a player an 'in<br>
character' tell <br>
to [mob] [message] : sends a mob a tell<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
This command is used to speak to others 'in character' and is in the<br>
language which you are currently speaking.  Often times, you can talk to<br>
various NPC's in the game which often starts with to [mob] [message]<br>
where the message is often 'hi' or 'hello'.  It is also used when you're<br>
in the portal room or Death to get transported to a city.  This is done<br>
by typing 'to [portal] [city]' or 'to [death] [city]'.<br>
<br>
Also see helpfiles on: tell, say, ask<br>
